{"tid":2323031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊思考下IZONE解散後既未來","createTime":"2020-12-12T22:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T07:58:35.000Z","uid":205928,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"07c21822c77cec738e0d8bea35c6c5836c5a2ca9","tid":2323031,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:16:41.000Z","msg":"真妹返星船新團做新一代大波+團欺隊長<br />\n英妹做新團長腿門面<br />\n搭幾件再加返件06 QQ妹做忙內<br />\n應該會小紅<br />\n<br />\n周間公司做開女演員<br />\n加埋周完美顏+完美身材+音樂中心經驗<br />\n點都有返一兩個女主角做下<br />\n紅唔紅就睇乜劇本+制作<br />\n但起碼有1.5線女主角紅度<br />\n<br />\n娜C入everglow做搞笑擔當<br />\n配合效果好Everglow人氣有機會再上一層樓<br />\n<br />\n車汪入Rocket punch做新門面<br />\nor maybe even Solo<br />\n唱跳顏都勁既車汪只要唔好比人雪藏<br />\n都應該幾掂下<br />\n<br />\n日本妹估計秋元康會出一啲用韓團經營手法既新團<br />\n成為46版系+48系之外既第三方勢力<br />\n再一步推動底層競爭<br />\n但自己喺上面食晒全部日本毒撚課金錢<br />\n諗吓都fat fat<br />\n<br />\n柔B 有stone music撐腰<br />\n加埋大主唱實力<br />\n有可能solo or maybe出啲類似bol4既新團<br />\n會唔會紅好難講<br />\n<br />\n彩燕同F隊好難講<br />\n多數應該退居幕後做trainee teacher<br />\n或者實力型producer +編舞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但無論最後大家會唔會成功<br />\n經歷如何<br />\nIZONE都會係佢哋心中最美嘅一段經歷同記憶🥃<br />\n如果大家接受都冇乜嘢嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBut...... still &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIZONE PERMANENT！！！"},{"pid":"8bcfa413f1a18e338fa1eac856b8af68f2166292","tid":2323031,"uid":308492,"like":20,"dislike":11,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:35:01.000Z","msg":"權F可以拍av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbed8f9fb06ae1bfd392dee52957ab8292e341a4","tid":2323031,"uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bcfa413f1a18e33